{"tid":2194122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快咇事件的啟示","createTime":"2020-09-08T10:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T10:55:07.000Z","uid":352454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0a810f91ec3940dc963739af2d7d956ec5844b","tid":2194122,"uid":352454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"1.中共想殺雞儆猴，嚇大家，等大家唔好再反。但你會問點解快咇？原因好簡單，之前捉d太出名的人，搞到國際反佢。所以明顯要找一d次一級出名的人。<br />\n2.另外，都可以顯示出中國對國際開始氣炎了。因為佢唔敢捉大粒野。<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋可以點做？就係令佢成為一級出名的人。之後無論誰比人搞，只要知名度高，佢就會好安全。"},{"pid":"9ba207de5152bf72eefb7d7018aea3ae2912ad10","tid":2194122,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"點做到？"},{"pid":"625583bc2e1be9185c80fc317779561a0be50cda","tid":2194122,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7463016f7a6b7a631aefe58d700fbcbda9d0a759","tid":2194122,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>tweet #fastbeat</strong>"},{"pid":"7a870a6031f97ea6dce74ebb10ece79d58b70dde","tid":2194122,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ba207de5152bf72eefb7d7018aea3ae2912ad10","tid":2194122,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"點做到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"佢本身都係娛樂界嘅人<br />\n要加強關注本應不難"},{"pid":"e8b99a901eb359c3d0a26db9208f3f9813fc719d","tid":2194122,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"港共見班街坊咁好反應就搵佢落單，但睇黎街坊好有機會反檯"},{"pid":"f7651a39eac9931677a1e65ad5bfeb0622eb45aa",